    class DefaultTokenMakerFactory
extends AbstractTokenMakerFactory
implements SyntaxConstants
    The default implementation of TokenMakerFactory. This factory can create TokenMakers for all languages known to RSyntaxTextArea.
    Version:
    1.0

      • initTokenMakerMap

        protected void initTokenMakerMap()
        Populates the mapping from keys to instances of TokenMakerCreators. Subclasses should override this method and call one of the putMapping overloads to register TokenMakers for syntax constants.
